Package ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team06

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    Builds the FitBit application.
    AwardData
    This class is used to check the squirrel badge(called Nutty), the time specific badges(called Early Bird and Night Owl), the triathalon badge(called Triple Threat), and the heartrate badge (called Healthy Heart) badge.
    CaloriesHistory
    Tracks the calories burned by the user.
    DailyGoals
    This class pulls the json info for the daily goals sections
    DailyTotals
    This class pulls the json info for the daily goals sections
    DistanceHistory
    Used to track and manage the user's distance travelled.
    ElevationHistory
    Used to manage and track the user's elevation climbed.
    FloorsHistory
    Used to track and manage the user's floor history.
    Goals
    Used to track and manage the user's goals.
    History
    Used to read and store the user's history.
    LifetimeTotals
    LifetimeTotals class that takes information from the api and saves it under the totals tab so the user can see their totals.
    MinFairHistory
    Used to track and manage the user's fairly active minutes history.
    MinLightHistory
    Used to track and manage the user's lightly active minutes history.
    MinSedentaryHistory
    Used to track and manage the user's sedantary minutes history.
    MinVeryHistory
    Used to track and manage the user's very active minutes history.
    Project
    Used to initialize the project.
    StepsHistory
    Used to track and manage the user's step count history.
    Totals
    Used to track and manage the user's lifetime totals.
    WeeklyGoals
    Used to track and manage the user's weekly goals.
    WeeklyTotals
    Used to track and manage the user's weekly totals.
